cs.NA, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.SI 

This paper deals with fast algorithms for computing statistical leverage scores and matrix coherence, which are important in various applications such as matrix completion and low-rank matrix approximation. These topics are closely related to numerical linear algebra (cs.NA) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves ideas from compressed sensing and dimensionality reduction (cs.DS, cs.IT), as well as streaming algorithms (cs.SI).
